  "text": "The time-fractional Kaup-Kupershmidt equation is expressed by the coordinates (x; t; u); thus, we want to reduce it using new coordinates. By introducing invariants (r; z), we obtain the new coordinates corresponding to the in nitesimal symmetry generator and we can reduce the mentioned equation [CITATION_1] . Consider a Lie point symmetry:",
